# ================================================================
# API ENDPOINT SUMMARY — JCT600
# ================================================================
# GET  /health                          → health check
# GET  /api/v1/vehicles/               → list & filter vehicles
# GET  /api/v1/vehicles/{id}           → vehicle detail
# POST /api/v1/vehicles/               → add vehicle (admin)
