# GET  /api/v1/bookings/service/{id}   → get service booking
# POST /api/v1/finance/part-exchange   → part-exchange valuation
# POST /api/v1/finance/calculator      → monthly finance calculator
# POST /api/v1/finance/apply           → submit finance application
